l The Rico Group has identified a set of key environmental and
social performance indicators and is in the process of developing
a comprehensive ESG roadmap. This roadmap will outline specific
commitments, well-defined goals, and measurable targets across
several focus areas, including:
l Assessment of GHG emissions across Scope 1, 2, and 3;
l Implementation of zero liquid discharge systems across all
manufacturing facilities;
l Promotion of diversity and inclusion within the organization;
l Strengthening the learning and development environment for
employees;
l Efficient water resource management;
l Sustainable waste management practices;
l Responsible supply chain management;
l Proactive stakeholder engagement;
l Ensuring employee health and workplace safety;
l Promoting innovation in products and processes;
l Engagement and development of local communities.

