Yes, the Rico Group is committed to providing a safe, respectful, and supportive workplace for all its employees and workers. To make sure any concerns are heard and addressed properly, several easy-to-access grievance redressal options are available, including:
l Grievance boxes placed at key locations across the premises;
l An Online Grievance Register for confidential and convenient submissions;
l Opportunities for employees to raise concerns through their trade union representatives
and internal committees;
l A dedicated grievance redressal email id: ethicsline@ricoauto.in, where employees
can directly share their issues with the concerned team.
These systems are in place to ensure that everyone has a fair and open way to voice their concerns. The Rico Group also reviews these processes regularly to keep improving how employee concerns are handled.

